<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Sign Up</title>
  </head>


  <div class="panel panel-default">
    <div class="panel-heading">
      <h1>Sign up here</h1>
      <h3>WEBrip Video the best links to all the best video online</h3>
      <p>
        Caution by siging up you agree to our Terms and Conditions
      </p>
    </div>

      <div class="panel-body">
        <%= form_for(resource, :as => resource_name, :url => registration_path(resource_name)) do |f| %>
        <%= devise_error_messages! %>

          <div class="form-group">
            <%= f.label :name %><i> - Type a User Name in this field, example: 'Mr Rails'</i>
            <%= f.text_field :name, autofocus: true, class: "form-control" %>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <%= f.label :email %><i> - Type a current email here, your email address is only needed for site fuctionality, it is not of public record.</i>
            <%= f.email_field :email, autofocus: true, class: "form-control" %>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <%= f.label :password %><i> - Pick a random password, see below intructions.</i>
            <%= f.password_field :password, class: "form-control" %>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <%= f.submit "Sign up", class: "btn btn-primary" %><i> - I agree to the Terms and Conditions.</i>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>

    <body>
      <div class="jumbotron center">
        <div class="container">

          <h2>How to sign up</h2>

          <h3>Name field</h3>

         <p>
            Above in the Name field, choose a User name. This can be anything you want to call yourself.
          </p>

          <h3>Email field</h3>

          <p>
            Provide your Email address example: you@gmail.com. Be sure to use a current and valid email that only you have access to. Enter into the Email field above.  
          </p>

          <h3>Password field</h3>

          <p>
            Choose a password in the above field Password. 'A good password is one that know one else may guess', so don't use anything like Birth dates, phone numbers, names of things you like, family names, and friends etc. A random password made up of really anything from A-Z , 0-9 and mix up a combination of say 10, example: Rs1headMp4. You should record your password and save it somwehere safe. 
          </p>

          <h3>Thank you for joining WEBrip Video</h3>
          <h2>The best links to all the best video downloads and streaming available online</h2>
        </div>
      </div><!--container-->
    </body>

    <div class="panel-footer">
        <p><i>..already a member ?</i></p>
        <%= link_to "Log in", new_user_session_path, class: "btn btn-danger btn-small" %>
      </div>
  </div>
</html>

